# Klinik Yönetim SaaS — Mimari Tasarım Dokümanı

Multi-tenant, randevu merkezli bir Klinik Yönetim SaaS ürünü için kapsamlı mimari tasarım.

---

## 1. Mimari Yaklaşım: Modüler Monolit

### Karar
**Modular Monolith** + **Clean/Hexagonal Architecture** hibrit yaklaşımı.

### Gerekçe

| Kriter | Modüler Monolit | Microservice |
|---|---|---|
| MVP hızı | ✅ Hızlı | ❌ Yavaş |
| Operasyonel yük | ✅ Düşük | ❌ Yüksek |
| Transaction bütünlüğü | ✅ Doğal | ❌ Saga pattern gerekir |
| Ölçeklenebilirlik | ✅ Yeterli (vertical) | ✅ Daha esnek |
| İleride ayrıştırma | ✅ Modül sınırları hazır | — |

**Her modül kendi domain sınırları içinde çalışır.** Modüller arası iletişim sadece tanımlı interface'ler ve event'ler üzerinden yapılır. Bu sayede ileride WhatsApp veya Finance modülü bağımsız servise dönüştürülebilir.

### Katman Yapısı (Her Modül İçin)

```
┌─────────────────────────────────┐
│         Presentation            │  ← Controller, DTO, Validation
├─────────────────────────────────┤
│         Application             │  ← Use Cases, Event Handlers
├─────────────────────────────────┤
│           Domain                │  ← Entity, Value Object, Domain Events
├─────────────────────────────────┤
│        Infrastructure           │  ← Repository impl, External APIs
└─────────────────────────────────┘
```

---

## 2. Tech Stack

### Backend

| Katman | Teknoloji | Gerekçe |
|---|---|---|
| Runtime | **Node.js 20 LTS** | Async I/O, WhatsApp webhook'lar için ideal, geniş ekosistem |
| Framework | **NestJS 10** | Modüler yapı doğal, DI container, Guard/Interceptor sistemi, enterprise-grade |
| Dil | **TypeScript 5.3+** | Tip güvenliği, domain modelleme, refactoring kolaylığı |
| ORM | **Prisma 5** | Type-safe query, migration, introspection, multi-schema desteği |
| Validation | **class-validator + class-transformer** | DTO validation, NestJS ile doğal entegrasyon |
| Auth | **JWT (access + refresh)** | Stateless, SaaS multi-tenant uyumlu |
| API Docs | **Swagger / OpenAPI 3.0** | NestJS `@nestjs/swagger` ile otomatik üretim |
| Realtime | **Socket.IO** (`@nestjs/websockets`) | Mesaj inbox'ı için, NestJS gateway desteği |
| Job Queue | **BullMQ + Redis** | Hold timeout, scheduled iptal, async webhook işleme |

### Database & Cache

| Bileşen | Teknoloji | Gerekçe |
|---|---|---|
| Primary DB | **PostgreSQL 16** | ACID, advisory lock, RLS, JSON desteği, olgun ekosistem |
| Cache / Queue | **Redis 7** | BullMQ backend, session cache, rate limiting |
| Tenant izolasyon | **Row-Level Security (RLS)** + `tenant_id` FK | Schema-per-tenant overkill, RLS performans ve güvenlik dengesini sağlar |

### DevOps / Tooling

| Bileşen | Teknoloji |
|---|---|
| Container | Docker + Docker Compose |
| Linting | ESLint + Prettier |
| Testing | Jest + Supertest |
| CI/CD | GitHub Actions (ileride) |
| Logging | Pino (structured JSON) |
| Monitoring | OpenTelemetry-ready (ileride) |

---

## 3. Veritabanı Şeması

### 3.1 Tenant & Auth

```sql
-- Klinik (Tenant)
CREATE TABLE clinics (
  id            UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
  name          VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  slug          VARCHAR(100) UNIQUE NOT NULL,  -- subdomain / identifier
  phone         VARCHAR(20),
  address       TEXT,
  timezone      VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'UTC',
  settings      JSONB DEFAULT '{}',            -- branş özelleştirme için genişleyebilir
  is_active     BOOLEAN NOT NULL DEFAULT true,
  created_at    TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now(),
  updated_at    TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now()
);

-- Kullanıcı
CREATE TABLE users (
  id            UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
  clinic_id     UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES clinics(id),
  email         VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  password_hash VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  first_name    VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  last_name     VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  phone         VARCHAR(20),
  role          VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL CHECK (role IN ('OWNER','DOCTOR','ASSISTANT','ACCOUNTANT')),
  is_active     BOOLEAN NOT NULL DEFAULT true,
  created_at    TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now(),
  updated_at    TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now(),
  UNIQUE(clinic_id, email)
);

-- Refresh Token (JWT)
CREATE TABLE refresh_tokens (
  id            UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
  user_id       UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES users(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
  token_hash    VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  expires_at    TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL,
  created_at    TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now()
);
```

### 3.2 Hasta Yönetimi

```sql
CREATE TABLE patients (
  id            UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
  clinic_id     UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES clinics(id),
  first_name    VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  last_name     VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  phone         VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL,
  email         VARCHAR(255),
  date_of_birth DATE,
  gender        VARCHAR(10),
  notes         TEXT,
  metadata      JSONB DEFAULT '{}',            -- branş spesifik ek alanlar
  is_active     BOOLEAN NOT NULL DEFAULT true,
  created_at    TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now(),
  updated_at    TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now(),
  UNIQUE(clinic_id, phone)                     -- aynı klinikte aynı telefon tekrarsız
);

CREATE INDEX idx_patients_search ON patients(clinic_id, last_name, first_name);
CREATE INDEX idx_patients_phone ON patients(clinic_id, phone);

-- Hasta Dosya Ekleri (meta bilgi, storage ileride S3/MinIO)
CREATE TABLE patient_attachments (
  id            UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
  clinic_id     UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES clinics(id),
  patient_id    UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES patients(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
  file_name     VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  file_type     VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  file_size     INTEGER NOT NULL,
  storage_key   VARCHAR(500) NOT NULL,          -- S3 key veya local path
  uploaded_by   UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES users(id),
  created_at    TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now()
);
```

### 3.3 Randevu Sistemi (Kritik)

```sql
-- Doktor Çalışma Saatleri
CREATE TABLE doctor_schedules (
  id            UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
  clinic_id     UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES clinics(id),
  doctor_id     UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES users(id),
  day_of_week   SMALLINT NOT NULL CHECK (day_of_week BETWEEN 0 AND 6), -- 0=Pzt
  start_time    TIME NOT NULL,
  end_time      TIME NOT NULL,
  slot_duration SMALLINT NOT NULL DEFAULT 30,   -- dakika
  is_active     BOOLEAN NOT NULL DEFAULT true,
  UNIQUE(clinic_id, doctor_id, day_of_week)
);

-- Randevu
CREATE TABLE appointments (
  id            UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
  clinic_id     UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES clinics(id),
  doctor_id     UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES users(id),
  patient_id    UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES patients(id),
  start_time    TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL,
  end_time      TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL,
  duration_min  SMALLINT NOT NULL,
  status        VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'HOLD'
                CHECK (status IN ('HOLD','CONFIRMED','CANCELLED','NO_SHOW','COMPLETED')),
  hold_until    TIMESTAMPTZ,                   -- HOLD durumunda son geçerlilik
  cancel_reason TEXT,
  notes         TEXT,
  created_by    UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES users(id),
  created_at    TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now(),
  updated_at    TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now(),

  -- ÇAKIŞMAYı DB SEVİYESİNDE ENGELLE (sadece aktif randevular)
  CONSTRAINT chk_time_range CHECK (end_time > start_time)
);

-- Çakışma engelleme indexi - Partial unique + exclusion constraint
-- GiST index ile range overlap kontrolü
CREATE EXTENSION IF NOT EXISTS btree_gist;

ALTER TABLE appointments ADD CONSTRAINT no_overlap_confirmed
  EXCLUDE USING gist (
    clinic_id WITH =,
    doctor_id WITH =,
    tstzrange(start_time, end_time) WITH &&
  )
  WHERE (status IN ('HOLD', 'CONFIRMED'));
```

> [!IMPORTANT]
> `EXCLUDE USING gist` constraint'i veritabanı seviyesinde randevu çakışmasını engelleyen en güvenilir yöntemdir. Application-level kontrol tek başına yeterli değildir — race condition riski vardır.

### 3.4 WhatsApp Mesajlaşma

```sql
-- Konuşma (telefon numarası bazlı)
CREATE TABLE conversations (
  id            UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
  clinic_id     UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES clinics(id),
  patient_id    UUID REFERENCES patients(id),
  wa_phone      VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL,          -- WhatsApp telefon numarası
  status        VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'BOT'
                CHECK (status IN ('BOT','HUMAN','CLOSED')),
  assigned_to   UUID REFERENCES users(id),     -- human takeover
  last_message_at TIMESTAMPTZ,
  created_at    TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now(),
  updated_at    TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now(),
  UNIQUE(clinic_id, wa_phone)
);

-- Mesajlar
CREATE TABLE messages (
  id            UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
  clinic_id     UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES clinics(id),
  conversation_id UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES conversations(id),
  wa_message_id VARCHAR(255),                  -- Meta API'den gelen ID (idempotency)
  direction     VARCHAR(10) NOT NULL CHECK (direction IN ('INBOUND','OUTBOUND')),
  content_type  VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'TEXT'
                CHECK (content_type IN ('TEXT','IMAGE','DOCUMENT','AUDIO','VIDEO','TEMPLATE')),
  body          TEXT,
  media_url     VARCHAR(500),
  status        VARCHAR(20) DEFAULT 'SENT'
                CHECK (status IN ('SENT','DELIVERED','READ','FAILED')),
  metadata      JSONB DEFAULT '{}',
  created_at    TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now()
);

-- Webhook idempotency (duplicate engelleme)
CREATE UNIQUE INDEX idx_messages_wa_id
  ON messages(clinic_id, wa_message_id)
  WHERE wa_message_id IS NOT NULL;

CREATE INDEX idx_messages_conversation ON messages(conversation_id, created_at DESC);
```

### 3.5 Finans / Tahsilat

```sql
CREATE TABLE payments (
  id            UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
  clinic_id     UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES clinics(id),
  patient_id    UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES patients(id),
  appointment_id UUID REFERENCES appointments(id), -- opsiyonel ilişki
  amount        DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL,
  currency      VARCHAR(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'TRY',
  payment_method VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL
                CHECK (payment_method IN ('CASH','CREDIT_CARD','BANK_TRANSFER','INSURANCE','OTHER')),
  payment_type  VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'PAYMENT'
                CHECK (payment_type IN ('PAYMENT','REFUND')),
  description   TEXT,
  paid_at       TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now(),
  created_by    UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES users(id),
  created_at    TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now()
);

CREATE INDEX idx_payments_patient ON payments(clinic_id, patient_id);

-- Bakiye View
CREATE VIEW patient_balances AS
SELECT
  clinic_id,
  patient_id,
  SUM(CASE WHEN payment_type = 'PAYMENT' THEN amount ELSE -amount END) AS total_paid
FROM payments
GROUP BY clinic_id, patient_id;
```

### 3.6 Klinik Notu / Reçete

```sql
CREATE TABLE clinical_notes (
  id            UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
  clinic_id     UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES clinics(id),
  patient_id    UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES patients(id),
  appointment_id UUID REFERENCES appointments(id),
  doctor_id     UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES users(id),
  note_type     VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'NOTE'
                CHECK (note_type IN ('NOTE','PRESCRIPTION','DIAGNOSIS')),
  title         VARCHAR(255),
  content       TEXT NOT NULL,
  visibility    VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'DOCTOR_ONLY'
                CHECK (visibility IN ('DOCTOR_ONLY','STAFF','ALL')),
  metadata      JSONB DEFAULT '{}',            -- branş spesifik veriler
  created_at    TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now(),
  updated_at    TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now()
);

CREATE INDEX idx_clinical_notes_patient ON clinical_notes(clinic_id, patient_id);
```

### 3.7 Audit Log

```sql
CREATE TABLE audit_logs (
  id            UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
  clinic_id     UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES clinics(id),
  user_id       UUID REFERENCES users(id),
  action        VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,           -- CREATE, UPDATE, DELETE, LOGIN, etc.
  entity_type   VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,           -- appointment, patient, payment, etc.
  entity_id     UUID,
  old_values    JSONB,
  new_values    JSONB,
  ip_address    VARCHAR(45),
  user_agent    TEXT,
  created_at    TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now()
);

CREATE INDEX idx_audit_logs_entity ON audit_logs(clinic_id, entity_type, entity_id);
CREATE INDEX idx_audit_logs_time ON audit_logs(clinic_id, created_at DESC);
```

### ER Diyagram

```mermaid
erDiagram
    CLINICS ||--o{ USERS : has
    CLINICS ||--o{ PATIENTS : has
    CLINICS ||--o{ APPOINTMENTS : has
    CLINICS ||--o{ CONVERSATIONS : has
    CLINICS ||--o{ PAYMENTS : has
    CLINICS ||--o{ AUDIT_LOGS : has

    USERS ||--o{ APPOINTMENTS : "doctor/creator"
    PATIENTS ||--o{ APPOINTMENTS : attends
    PATIENTS ||--o{ PAYMENTS : pays
    PATIENTS ||--o{ CLINICAL_NOTES : "has notes"
    PATIENTS ||--o{ PATIENT_ATTACHMENTS : "has files"

    APPOINTMENTS ||--o| PAYMENTS : "linked to"
    APPOINTMENTS ||--o| CLINICAL_NOTES : "linked to"

    CONVERSATIONS ||--o{ MESSAGES : contains
    PATIENTS ||--o| CONVERSATIONS : "linked via phone"
```

