## 5. API Endpoint Listesi

Tüm endpoint'ler `/api/v1` prefix'i altındadır. Tenant `clinic_id` JWT token'dan alınır.

### 5.1 Auth

| Method | Endpoint | Açıklama | Erişim |
|---|---|---|---|
| POST | `/auth/register` | Klinik + OWNER kaydı | Public |
| POST | `/auth/login` | Giriş (JWT döner) | Public |
| POST | `/auth/refresh` | Token yenile | Auth |
| POST | `/auth/logout` | Çıkış (refresh token iptal) | Auth |
| GET | `/auth/me` | Mevcut kullanıcı bilgisi | Auth |

### 5.2 Tenant

| Method | Endpoint | Açıklama | Erişim |
|---|---|---|---|
| GET | `/clinic` | Klinik bilgisi | Auth |
| PATCH | `/clinic` | Klinik güncelle | OWNER |
| GET | `/clinic/settings` | Ayarları getir | OWNER |
| PATCH | `/clinic/settings` | Ayarları güncelle | OWNER |

### 5.3 Kullanıcı Yönetimi

| Method | Endpoint | Açıklama | Erişim |
|---|---|---|---|
| GET | `/users` | Kullanıcıları listele | OWNER, ASSISTANT |
| POST | `/users` | Kullanıcı ekle | OWNER |
| GET | `/users/:id` | Kullanıcı detay | OWNER, Self |
| PATCH | `/users/:id` | Kullanıcı güncelle | OWNER |
| DELETE | `/users/:id` | Kullanıcı deaktif et | OWNER |

### 5.4 Hasta Yönetimi

| Method | Endpoint | Açıklama | Erişim |
|---|---|---|---|
| GET | `/patients` | Hastaları listele & ara | OWNER, DOCTOR, ASSISTANT |
| POST | `/patients` | Hasta ekle | OWNER, DOCTOR, ASSISTANT |
| GET | `/patients/:id` | Hasta detay | OWNER, DOCTOR, ASSISTANT |
| PATCH | `/patients/:id` | Hasta güncelle | OWNER, DOCTOR, ASSISTANT |
| DELETE | `/patients/:id` | Hasta deaktif et | OWNER |
| GET | `/patients/:id/appointments` | Hasta randevuları | OWNER, DOCTOR, ASSISTANT |
| GET | `/patients/:id/payments` | Hasta ödemeleri | OWNER, ACCOUNTANT |
| GET | `/patients/:id/balance` | Hasta bakiye | OWNER, ACCOUNTANT |
| POST | `/patients/:id/attachments` | Dosya yükle | OWNER, DOCTOR, ASSISTANT |
| GET | `/patients/:id/attachments` | Dosyaları listele | OWNER, DOCTOR, ASSISTANT |

### 5.5 Randevu Sistemi ⭐

| Method | Endpoint | Açıklama | Erişim |
|---|---|---|---|
| GET | `/appointments` | Randevuları listele (filtreleme) | OWNER, DOCTOR, ASSISTANT |
| POST | `/appointments` | Randevu oluştur (HOLD) | OWNER, DOCTOR, ASSISTANT |
| GET | `/appointments/:id` | Randevu detay | OWNER, DOCTOR, ASSISTANT |
| PATCH | `/appointments/:id/confirm` | HOLD → CONFIRMED | OWNER, DOCTOR, ASSISTANT |
| PATCH | `/appointments/:id/cancel` | İptal et | OWNER, DOCTOR, ASSISTANT |
| PATCH | `/appointments/:id/no-show` | No-show işaretle | OWNER, DOCTOR |
| PATCH | `/appointments/:id/complete` | Tamamlandı | OWNER, DOCTOR |
| GET | `/appointments/available-slots` | Müsait slotları getir | OWNER, DOCTOR, ASSISTANT |
| GET | `/doctors/:id/schedule` | Doktor takvimi | OWNER, DOCTOR, ASSISTANT |
| PUT | `/doctors/:id/schedule` | Doktor takvim güncelle | OWNER, DOCTOR |

### 5.6 WhatsApp Mesajlaşma

| Method | Endpoint | Açıklama | Erişim |
|---|---|---|---|
| POST | `/webhooks/whatsapp` | Meta webhook (inbound) | Public (verify) |
| GET | `/conversations` | Konuşma listesi (inbox) | OWNER, ASSISTANT |
| GET | `/conversations/:id` | Konuşma detay + mesajlar | OWNER, ASSISTANT |
| POST | `/conversations/:id/messages` | Mesaj gönder | OWNER, ASSISTANT |
| PATCH | `/conversations/:id/assign` | Operatöre ata | OWNER, ASSISTANT |
| PATCH | `/conversations/:id/mode` | BOT ↔ HUMAN mode | OWNER, ASSISTANT |

### 5.7 Finans / Tahsilat

| Method | Endpoint | Açıklama | Erişim |
|---|---|---|---|
| GET | `/payments` | Ödemeleri listele | OWNER, ACCOUNTANT |
| POST | `/payments` | Ödeme kaydet | OWNER, ACCOUNTANT |
| GET | `/payments/:id` | Ödeme detay | OWNER, ACCOUNTANT |
| GET | `/payments/summary` | Özet rapor | OWNER, ACCOUNTANT |

### 5.8 Klinik Notu / Reçete

| Method | Endpoint | Açıklama | Erişim |
|---|---|---|---|
| GET | `/clinical-notes` | Notları listele | OWNER, DOCTOR |
| POST | `/clinical-notes` | Not oluştur | DOCTOR |
| GET | `/clinical-notes/:id` | Not detay | OWNER, DOCTOR |
| PATCH | `/clinical-notes/:id` | Not güncelle | DOCTOR (kendi) |

### 5.9 Audit Log

| Method | Endpoint | Açıklama | Erişim |
|---|---|---|---|
| GET | `/audit-logs` | Logları listele | OWNER |
| GET | `/audit-logs/:entityType/:entityId` | Entity bazlı log | OWNER |

---

## 6. Randevu Çakışma Algoritması — Detaylı Tasarım

En kritik modül olan randevu sistemi için **3 katmanlı savunma** stratejisi:

### Katman 1: Application-Level Kontrol

```typescript
// appointment-conflict.service.ts — Pseudocode

async checkAvailability(
  clinicId: string,
  doctorId: string,
  startTime: Date,
  endTime: Date,
  excludeAppointmentId?: string
): Promise<{ available: boolean; conflicts: Appointment[] }> {

  const conflicts = await prisma.appointment.findMany({
    where: {
      clinic_id: clinicId,
      doctor_id: doctorId,
      status: { in: ['HOLD', 'CONFIRMED'] },
      id: excludeAppointmentId ? { not: excludeAppointmentId } : undefined,
      // Overlap kontrolü: A.start < B.end AND A.end > B.start
      start_time: { lt: endTime },
      end_time: { gt: startTime },
    },
  });

  return {
    available: conflicts.length === 0,
    conflicts,
  };
}
```

### Katman 2: PostgreSQL Exclusion Constraint (Nihai Güvenlik)

```sql
-- Veritabanı seviyesinde overlap kesinlikle engellenir
ALTER TABLE appointments ADD CONSTRAINT no_overlap_confirmed
  EXCLUDE USING gist (
    clinic_id WITH =,
    doctor_id WITH =,
    tstzrange(start_time, end_time) WITH &&
  )
  WHERE (status IN ('HOLD', 'CONFIRMED'));
```

Concurrent iki request aynı slota yazarsa, ikincisi **DB exception** alır — uygulama bunu yakalar ve kullanıcıya "slot dolu" yanıtı döner.

### Katman 3: Advisory Lock (Yüksek Yoğunluk Senaryosu)

```typescript
// Aynı doktor+gün kombinasyonu için serialization
async createAppointmentSafe(dto: CreateAppointmentDto) {
  const lockKey = this.generateLockKey(dto.doctorId, dto.startTime);

  return await this.prisma.$transaction(async (tx) => {
    // 1. Advisory lock al (aynı doktor-gün için seri işlem)
    await tx.$executeRaw`SELECT pg_advisory_xact_lock(${lockKey})`;

    // 2. Application-level kontrol
    const available = await this.checkAvailability(
      dto.clinicId, dto.doctorId, dto.startTime, dto.endTime
    );
    if (!available) throw new ConflictException('Slot dolu');

    // 3. INSERT (DB constraint son savunma hattı)
    return await tx.appointment.create({ data: { ...dto, status: 'HOLD' } });

    // 4. Transaction commit → advisory lock otomatik release
  });
}

private generateLockKey(doctorId: string, date: Date): number {
  // UUID'den deterministik integer üret (doktor + gün bazlı)
  const hash = createHash('md5')
    .update(`${doctorId}-${date.toISOString().split('T')[0]}`)
    .digest();
  return hash.readInt32BE(0);
}
```

### Hold → Timeout Akışı

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> HOLD: Randevu oluştur
    HOLD --> CONFIRMED: Onayla (hold süresi içinde)
    HOLD --> CANCELLED: Manuel iptal
    HOLD --> CANCELLED: Hold süresi doldu (BullMQ job)
    CONFIRMED --> COMPLETED: Randevu tamamlandı
    CONFIRMED --> CANCELLED: İptal edildi
    CONFIRMED --> NO_SHOW: Hasta gelmedi
    COMPLETED --> [*]
    CANCELLED --> [*]
    NO_SHOW --> [*]
```

**BullMQ Hold Timeout İşleyici:**

```typescript
// appointment-hold.processor.ts
@Processor('appointment-hold')
export class AppointmentHoldProcessor {
  @Process('expire-hold')
  async handleHoldExpiry(job: Job<{ appointmentId: string }>) {
    const appointment = await this.prisma.appointment.findUnique({
      where: { id: job.data.appointmentId },
    });

    if (appointment?.status === 'HOLD') {
      await this.prisma.appointment.update({
        where: { id: appointment.id },
        data: { status: 'CANCELLED', cancel_reason: 'HOLD_EXPIRED' },
      });
      // Event emit → bildirim gönderilebilir
      this.eventEmitter.emit('appointment.holdExpired', appointment);
    }
  }
}
```

Randevu `HOLD` olarak oluşturulduğunda:
```typescript
await this.holdQueue.add('expire-hold',
  { appointmentId: appointment.id },
  { delay: HOLD_DURATION_MS } // ör: 15 dakika = 900_000 ms
);
```

